- Phase 2 (PRD-02): Marie AI, smart routing, predictive alerts, analytics, push notifications
- Phase 3 (PRD-03): Compliance (DOT + non-DOT), fleet management, logistics CRM
- Phase 4 (PRD-04): Multi-tenant billing (Stripe), onboarding wizard, mobile polish, reports, accessibility, launch readiness

